snippet.title: Kung-Fu LIVE release date announcement trailer
snippet.description: Kung-Fu LIVE, the ultimate full-body motion fighting game is coming to PlayStation Network (PS3) on December 7th and 8th respectively in the USA and Europe. Get yours and start kicking some serious ASS!
